---
title: Veggie Gyoza & Sticky Sriracha Chicken Noodles with Asian Greens & Crispy Shallots
description: Put down that phone and throw out the takeaway menu because you won’t be needing them anymore! We’ve got a
gyoza and chicken noodle wonder ready to go tonight - all you have to do is pop the gyoza in a pan and serve them atop a bed of
Asian greens and sticky, slurpable noodles.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
